//[Reference] 'Oh! I...I didn't expect to see you here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000100=あら！こんなところで会うなんて…
//[Reference] 'Uh... How did you even get here? Those devices are one time use and rather hard to make...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000200=それに…どうやってここへ？あの装置は1度しか使えないし、作るのも大変なはず…
//[Reference] 'It was that ^c:1486b0;scientist^c:pop;, wasn't it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000300=あの^c:1486b0;科学者^c:pop;でしょ？
//[Reference] 'I just wanted to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; back, you know?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000400=私はただ、^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;に戻ってきてほしいだけなの。
//[Reference] 'We all wanted that, but he just wouldn't come...kept talking about duty in his letters...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000500=私たちのたったひとつの願い、それすら彼は応えてくれなかった…手紙で話すのは仕事のことばかりだし。
//[Reference] 'It was really hard to build something that could transfer objects from place to place!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000600=転送装置の開発は本当に大変だったんだから！
//[Reference] 'It was one-time-use too...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000700=おまけに使えるのは1度きりだし…
//[Reference] 'How did she even fix it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000800=あの人、どうやって装置を直したの？
//[Reference] 'Well never mind. You're here now.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10000900=まあいいわ。現に今あなたはここにいるわけだし。
//[Reference] 'At least one of you came willingly...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001000=あなたみたいに自分から来てくれる人もいるのね…
//[Reference] 'I'm here to bring ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop; back.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001100=^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;を連れ戻しに来たんだ。
//[Reference] 'Oh...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001200=へえ…
//[Reference] 'I shouldn't really help you, but...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001300=本当はあなたの話に乗るのは気が引けるけど…
//[Reference] 'It's hard to see him so distressed.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001400=彼が苦しむ姿を見るのは辛いわ。
//[Reference] 'Perhaps it was truly wrong of me to drag him back. Maybe he'll come back of his own free will someday...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001500=無理やり連れ戻すのは間違いだったのね。いつか自分の意志で帰ってきてくれるのを待つしかないか…
//[Reference] 'Alright. I'll help you. It won't be easy though...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001600=分かった。手を貸すわ。簡単にはいかないと思うけど…
//[Reference] 'We didn't want him to run away so we moved him somewhere...special...for the time being.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001700=彼には逃げ出されると困るから、とりあえず…その…特別な部屋で休んでもらってるの。
//[Reference] 'If you could get me a few items I should be able to pull together something that will whisk you past the barrier.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001800=アイテムを何個か持ってきてくれたら、バリアを通り抜けられる道具を作れると思うわ。
//[Reference] 'There should be ^c:d03e37;five components^c:pop;. If you look around the ^c:1486b0;tree houses^c:pop; here you should find them.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10001900=必要な^c:d03e37;部品は5つ^c:pop;。^c:1486b0;ツリーハウス^c:pop;の周辺で見つかるはずよ。
//[Reference] 'We shouldn't be seen talking until you find the ^c:d03e37;five components^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002000=^c:d03e37;5つの部品^c:pop;が見つかるまでは、お互い他人のフリをしていましょう。
//[Reference] 'It would be bad if they suspected something was happening...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002100=みんなに怪しまれたらまずいことになるしね…
//[Reference] 'Yes, this looks like everything we need!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002200=やった、必要なものがそろったわ！
//[Reference] 'Now if you just give me a minu-'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002300=じゃあちょっと時間をちょうだ…
//[Reference] 'I apologise, the device initiated before I was quite ready.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002400=ごめんなさい、ちゃんと準備できる前に装置が起動しちゃったみたい。
//[Reference] 'I hope I didn't cause you too much unnecessary concern...?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002500=まあなんとか無事っぽいし、大丈夫かな…？
//[Reference] 'Who are you? Are you here to sell us something?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002600=あなたは誰？何か売りに来たの？
//[Reference] 'Just so you know, we don't have much money here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002700=念のために言っておくけど、私たちにはあまりお金がないの…
//[Reference] 'Too much being spent on personal projects and maintenence you see...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002800=個人的なこととか、メンテナンスとかに使い過ぎちゃって…
//[Reference] 'Oh! You know ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002900=あら！^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;を知ってるの？
//[Reference] 'I hope he is doing well. I haven't seen him in a long time.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10002910=彼、元気だといいけど。長いこと会ってないのよね。
//[Reference] 'Well... I can send you back. But I don't think I have enough parts to visit myself...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003000=それじゃあまあ…送り返してあげるわ。でも、私まで行けるほどのパーツは無いのよね…
//[Reference] 'Do you want to go?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003100=行きたい？
//[Reference] 'Yep!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003200=うん！
//[Reference] 'No. I wanna look around.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003300=いや、ちょっと見て回りたい。
//[Reference] 'Oh! I...I didn't expect to see you here...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003400=あら！こ…こんなところで会うなんて…
//[Reference] 'Uh... How did you even get here?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003500=えーと…そもそもどうやってここに来たの？
//[Reference] 'Did your ^c:1486b0;scientist^c:pop; give that device to you?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003600=^c:1486b0;科学者^c:pop;にその装置をもらったの？
//[Reference] 'I was sure that they would give it to ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003700=てっきり^c:1486b0;レイフ^c:pop;に渡してると思ってたのになあ…
//[Reference] 'When you go back, can you tell them to work on it some more?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003800=戻ったら、もうちょっと頑張れって伝えておいてくれない？
//[Reference] 'There's a teleporter in the tree, that you can use to get back home.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003810=あの木の中にあるテレポーターを使えば、家に帰れるわ。
//[Reference] 'I wish I could come too... But that teleporter doesn't work for us.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003820=私も行けたら良かったんだけど…あのテレポーターは、私たちじゃ使えないのよね。
//[Reference] 'Sure!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10003900=もちろん！
//[Reference] 'Nope.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004000=いやです。
//[Reference] 'How are you still here? Did something fail?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004100=どうしてまだここにいるの？何か失敗したの？
//[Reference] 'These teleporters sure are finicky aren't they...'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004200=そのテレポーターは本当に厄介ね…
//[Reference] 'Do you want me to try and send you back again?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004300=また送り返してあげよっか？
//[Reference] 'Yep!'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004400=うん！
//[Reference] 'No. I wanna look around.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004500=いや、ちょっと見て回りたい。
//[Reference] 'Alright then. See you again soon.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004600=分かったわ。またね。
//[Reference] 'Are you sure?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004700=本当に大丈夫？
//[Reference] 'Well... come back to me when you want to leave then.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004800=じゃあ…帰りたくなったら戻って来てね。
//[Reference] 'Huh... how did that not work?'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10004900=う～ん…どうして上手くいかなかったのかしら？
//[Reference] 'Give me a moment to see if I can get it working.'
staxel.village.dialogue.RemVillage.line:10005000=ちょっと時間をちょうだい。なんとかしてみるわ。
